instancecontenttextdata_ids_17404_Text: No good. It's protected by some kind of barrier.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17406_Text: Ooh, barriers are my specialty! I'll have this down before you know it!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17408_Text: Chief, something's happening with the cube!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17409_Text: Oho, so it changes into a life-form, and a hostile one at that.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17410_Text: We'll see to the creature! Wedge, keep at the barrier! Biggs, watch his back!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17411_Text: Another one! It seems they'll continue spawning so long as the monitor is operational.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17414_Text: Hah, it's out of commission! The trick is to reverse the barrier's energy current!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17415_Text: Well done, Wedge! That leaves just the enemy!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17418_Text: Chief, the second cube's about to turn!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17419_Text: Let's finish it quickly and be on our way.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17420_Text: Right, the same approach as before. Wedge and Biggs, the monitor is yours.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17422_Text: Be careful! The cubes are going to turn!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17423_Text: Damn, they're spawning fast! Hurry, Wedge!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17424_Text: Another monitor down and out! Am I in form today or what!?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17425_Text: That you are, Wedge! Now, give us a moment while we clean things up.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17426_Text: Biggs, this time you get a monitor as well. <Split([ObjectParameter(1)], ,1)/>, you know what to do.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17427_Text: Hmph, I should think I'm no less qualified to tinker with these toys.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17430_Text: Have care. I sense a formidable presence.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17431_Text: A behemoth!? We're going to have to roll up our sleeves!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17432_Text: Never one for half measures...eh, Omega?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_17434_Text: Mine too! That should take care of the cubes!
